skins.shipDescription: Type B1 cruiser submarine C I-19.
skins.selfIntroduction: Destroyers, carriers, battleships, I'll sink 'em all with one shot~! Hey, Commander, aren't I amazing? I am, right?
skins.acquisition: I'm I-19! Commaaandeeer! I-19's been waiting so, so long for you~!
skins.login: Commander! I've been waiting sooooo long for you!
skins.details: Did you want to see me? Hehehe~ That makes me super happy~
skins.secretaryIdle1: I made hot tea for you! I'm so great, aren't I?
skins.secretaryIdle2: I went through your paperwork! Hehehe~ Maybe you could pat me on the head as a reward~
skins.secretaryTouch: Do you want me to help you relax?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Hehehe~ I don't mind at all, as long as you praise me~

skins.shipDescription: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?
skins.acquisition: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?
skins.login: School's so boring... I'd rather be by your side, Commander~ Hehehe~
skins.details: I should make some friends? But I don't need any~! You're the only person I need!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Eek! The wind nearly... Hmm? Were you trying to sneak a peek~?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, help me with my extra lessons...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Do you like my outfit, Commander? Is it cute? Hehehe~
skins.secretaryTouch: Hehehe~ Do you wanna walk to and from school with me?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: No touching until everyone else has gone home...
